==English==
===Transitive verb===
'''to elect''' (''[[present participle]]'' '''electing''', ''[[past tense]] and [[past participle]]'' '''elected''')

# To choose or make a decision (to do something)
# To choose (a candidate) in an election

====Translations====
*Danish: [[vælge]] (1,2)
*Swedish: [[välja]] (1,2)
*Portuguese: [[eleger]]

===Adjective===
'''elect''' (''no [[comparative]] or [[superlative]] forms'')

#(''used only after the noun'') Who has just been elected in the specified post.
#:''He is the president elect.''

====Translations====
*Swedish: [[vald]]

